column16: Mike Trout strikes out on a foul tip.
Shane Robinson out on a sacrifice fly to right fielder Aaron Altherr.   Kaleb Cowart scores.
Kaleb Cowart singles on a ground ball to right fielder Aaron Altherr.   Cliff Pennington to 2nd.
Cliff Pennington singles on a line drive to center fielder Odubel Herrera.
Martin Maldonado flies out to center fielder Odubel Herrera.
